Description: Papyrus written with black ink with demotic legal text on recto (15 ll.) and names of 10 witnesses on verso. Thompson's MS Catalogue: "Gift o f1/8 share of a house by Petetumis sohn of Twot to his daughter Teteimuthes. Date year 25 Paophi(?) 21(?) of Ptolemy Epiphanes = BC 181 Nov. 26". Nos. 10575-10601 from the Siut Archive.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (2741) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/2741)
